'''Holly''' is the mother of [[Kelsey]].

==History==
Holly's daughter, Kelsey, had cystic fibrosis, which had damaged her lungs, liver, and pancreas, necessitating transplant. A good match became available, so Kelsey was taken into surgery. The transplant was successful and she was stable afterward.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married to [[Nick (I Am Not Waiting Anymore)|Nick]].
